1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:10,000
[English subtitles are available]

2
00:01:36,470 --> 00:01:41,000
[Strange Tales of Tang Dynasty II To the West]

3
00:01:41,500 --> 00:01:43,979
[Episode 22]

4
00:01:52,070 --> 00:01:52,800
Who's there?

5
00:01:56,310 --> 00:01:56,870
You're back.

6
00:01:56,870 --> 00:01:57,600
Lu Lingfeng?

7
00:02:00,470 --> 00:02:01,440
When I was down the mountain,

8
00:02:01,440 --> 00:02:02,790
I startled a nest of pheasants,

9
00:02:02,790 --> 00:02:04,260
so I brought several of them back.

10
00:02:04,260 --> 00:02:05,470
Since you weren't home,

11
00:02:05,470 --> 00:02:07,070
I went ahead and stewed them.

12
00:02:09,110 --> 00:02:09,949
Lu Lingfeng.

13
00:02:20,670 --> 00:02:22,400
I heard there are pheasants...

14
00:02:25,270 --> 00:02:26,190
General Lu.

15
00:02:26,550 --> 00:02:28,120
I didn't know you were so capable.

16
00:02:28,120 --> 00:02:29,720
You even know how to cook now.

17
00:02:32,520 --> 00:02:34,870
It does smell quite good.

18
00:02:35,430 --> 00:02:37,490
When it's ready, bring it over for us.

19
00:02:48,750 --> 00:02:49,680
Alright, Xijun.

20
00:02:50,350 --> 00:02:51,829
I'm back now, aren't I?

21
00:02:52,510 --> 00:02:54,630
You almost scared me to death.

22
00:02:56,390 --> 00:02:57,130
Don't cry.

23
00:03:01,150 --> 00:03:02,990
Have your late night snack first.

24
00:03:02,990 --> 00:03:04,510
I have something important to ask of you

25
00:03:04,510 --> 00:03:05,790
later.

26
00:03:12,790 --> 00:03:14,830
How could this happen?

27
00:03:22,860 --> 00:03:24,860
Master, there's no need to be angry.

28
00:03:24,990 --> 00:03:27,590
Promoting those who contribute to Taiyin Sect

29
00:03:27,670 --> 00:03:28,790
was my idea.

30
00:03:29,510 --> 00:03:30,590
It's understandable that

31
00:03:30,590 --> 00:03:32,700
Yuan He resorted to this vicious tactic

32
00:03:32,700 --> 00:03:34,230
because he was worried that

33
00:03:34,230 --> 00:03:36,110
I'd take over his position as the lieutenant.

34
00:03:36,110 --> 00:03:39,040
If it weren't for the fact that we are short-staffed,

35
00:03:39,470 --> 00:03:42,579
I would throw him into the Delicacy Cave right away.

36
00:03:49,400 --> 00:03:50,470
That Lu Lingfeng

37
00:03:50,670 --> 00:03:52,600
actually managed to escape death.

38
00:03:52,750 --> 00:03:55,410
If we don't kill him, he'll become a big trouble.

39
00:03:55,670 --> 00:03:56,950
I actually brought him into the mountains this time

40
00:03:56,950 --> 00:03:57,910
to test him.

41
00:03:58,310 --> 00:03:59,320
The conclusion is,

42
00:03:59,320 --> 00:04:00,910
this person is definitely not sent by the court

43
00:04:00,910 --> 00:04:01,750
against us.

44
00:04:02,310 --> 00:04:03,870
If you misjudged him,

45
00:04:05,350 --> 00:04:07,590
do you know what the consequences will be?

46
00:04:07,590 --> 00:04:08,300
Of course.

47
00:04:09,760 --> 00:04:12,620
I, Linghu Shuo, am willing to stake my life on it that

48
00:04:13,310 --> 00:04:14,020
Lu Lingfeng

49
00:04:14,420 --> 00:04:15,390
can be trusted.

50
00:04:52,790 --> 00:04:54,790
Why did you risk your life to save me?

51
00:04:54,870 --> 00:04:56,350
Hasn't it ever occurred to you that

52
00:04:56,350 --> 00:04:57,390
if I go back alive,

53
00:04:57,590 --> 00:04:59,310
Taiyin Sect won't let you go?

54
00:05:03,030 --> 00:05:04,470
But if you fell to your death,

55
00:05:04,470 --> 00:05:06,930
who would take me to see the real sect leader?

56
00:05:11,550 --> 00:05:13,750
Your identity as a spy has been exposed.

57
00:05:14,110 --> 00:05:15,230
Stop lying.

58
00:05:17,110 --> 00:05:18,110
Who said I'm a spy?

59
00:05:18,430 --> 00:05:20,100
Chang'an is expecting my head.

60
00:05:20,100 --> 00:05:21,870
Even if Mount Taiyin is wiped out,

61
00:05:21,870 --> 00:05:24,600
the credit will still go to the state government.

62
00:05:25,150 --> 00:05:27,010
The court still won't believe me.

63
00:05:27,470 --> 00:05:28,470
If I, Lu Lingfeng,

64
00:05:28,790 --> 00:05:30,650
want to achieve something great,

65
00:05:31,190 --> 00:05:33,650
I definitely can't rely on the court of Tang.

66
00:05:34,710 --> 00:05:36,470
It's a pity that all the blood and tears

67
00:05:36,470 --> 00:05:37,930
I shed for Tang was a waste.

68
00:05:39,200 --> 00:05:40,050
So why didn't you draw

69
00:05:40,050 --> 00:05:42,720
the Map of Western Region's Troop Locations just now?

70
00:05:42,720 --> 00:05:43,430
Firstly,

71
00:05:44,090 --> 00:05:46,350
I don't believe that bald man is the sect leader.

72
00:05:46,350 --> 00:05:46,950
Secondly,

73
00:05:47,260 --> 00:05:50,070
although I have the map of troop locations memorized,

74
00:05:50,070 --> 00:05:51,070
I couldn't draw it

75
00:05:52,510 --> 00:05:54,770
because I simply don't know how to paint.

76
00:05:56,270 --> 00:05:58,190
Among those who came to Hanzhou with him,

77
00:05:58,190 --> 00:05:59,990
there's a woman named Pei Xijun.

78
00:06:00,910 --> 00:06:01,790
She's good at Danqing,

79
00:06:01,790 --> 00:06:04,320
and she and Lu Lingfeng can read each other's minds.

80
00:06:04,320 --> 00:06:05,580
She can draw it for him.

81
00:06:06,510 --> 00:06:09,910
If that's really the case, it would be great.

82
00:06:10,190 --> 00:06:11,710
We agreed to meet

83
00:06:12,070 --> 00:06:13,870
at Tianbao Restaurant in 2 days.

84
00:06:13,910 --> 00:06:14,670
By then,

85
00:06:15,190 --> 00:06:17,120
if he still can't hand over the map,

86
00:06:18,150 --> 00:06:19,590
I know what to do.

87
00:06:30,090 --> 00:06:31,690
I know it takes at least 2 days

88
00:06:31,790 --> 00:06:33,560
for an ordinary person to do such a painting.

89
00:06:33,560 --> 00:06:34,350
But this map concerns

90
00:06:34,350 --> 00:06:35,610
the safety of Hanzhou,

91
00:06:35,710 --> 00:06:36,970
so it can't be delayed.

92
00:06:37,510 --> 00:06:38,750
I hope you can finish it

93
00:06:38,750 --> 00:06:40,280
as soon as possible, Xijun.

94
00:06:40,990 --> 00:06:41,720
Don't worry.

95
00:06:41,990 --> 00:06:43,590
As long as you describe it clearly,

96
00:06:43,590 --> 00:06:44,350
I can definitely finish it

97
00:06:44,350 --> 00:06:45,150
before dawn.

98
00:06:45,550 --> 00:06:46,110
Okay.

99
00:06:55,590 --> 00:06:56,720
Why are you smiling?

100
00:06:58,550 --> 00:06:59,710
This is

101
00:07:00,320 --> 00:07:01,410
[Troop Locations and Arming Map of Mount Taiyin]

102
00:07:00,750 --> 00:07:02,950
the first time you and I paint together.

103
00:07:18,270 --> 00:07:18,830
How's it?

104
00:07:20,710 --> 00:07:22,110
The pheasant tastes

105
00:07:22,270 --> 00:07:23,470
quite unique.

106
00:07:24,840 --> 00:07:26,550
The General of the Imperial Guards from the Lu family of Fanyang

107
00:07:26,550 --> 00:07:27,810
stewed chicken for me.

108
00:07:28,150 --> 00:07:28,790
Not bad.

109
00:07:29,180 --> 00:07:30,360
Not bad at all.

110
00:07:30,990 --> 00:07:32,320
If you like it, eat more.

111
00:07:32,630 --> 00:07:33,110
But

112
00:07:33,310 --> 00:07:34,570
you'd better be quiet.

113
00:07:34,670 --> 00:07:35,930
Don't distract Xijun.

114
00:07:36,920 --> 00:07:38,920
I shouldn't have complimented you.

115
00:07:49,250 --> 00:07:50,450
What are you reading?

116
00:07:52,590 --> 00:07:54,190
This is the file

117
00:07:54,260 --> 00:07:56,400
from 18 years ago

118
00:07:56,430 --> 00:07:57,670
when Taiyin Sect was exterminated.

119
00:07:57,670 --> 00:07:58,800
Where did you get it?

120
00:07:59,750 --> 00:08:00,770
Of course I didn't go to

121
00:08:00,770 --> 00:08:02,370
the Commandery for nothing.

122
00:08:03,390 --> 00:08:06,310
The mastermind behind the rebellion at that time

123
00:08:06,460 --> 00:08:09,050
was the great-grandson of Duan Gui.

124
00:08:09,270 --> 00:08:10,970
After he was executed by the court,

125
00:08:10,970 --> 00:08:13,070
there was no more rebellion of Taiyin Sect

126
00:08:13,070 --> 00:08:15,030
in Hanzhou for 15 years.

127
00:08:15,990 --> 00:08:17,030
Check this out.

128
00:08:17,790 --> 00:08:20,870
Among the rebels at that time,

129
00:08:21,170 --> 00:08:23,190
there was a seven-year-old girl

130
00:08:23,270 --> 00:08:24,150
who escaped.

131
00:08:25,150 --> 00:08:27,910
She was the daughter of the so-called sect leader.

132
00:08:27,910 --> 00:08:30,870
This little girl rode a saw-toothed rhino

133
00:08:31,070 --> 00:08:33,070
and escaped deep into the mountains.

134
00:08:33,070 --> 00:08:34,240
It was later rumored that

135
00:08:34,240 --> 00:08:36,950
she was adopted by a huntsman surnamed Song.

136
00:08:39,270 --> 00:08:42,080
After that, the government troops searched in the mountains for many years,

137
00:08:42,080 --> 00:08:43,200
but they never found this

138
00:08:43,200 --> 00:08:44,600
huntsman surnamed Song.

139
00:08:46,910 --> 00:08:47,710
Wait a minute.

140
00:08:48,350 --> 00:08:50,110
His surname is Song?

141
00:08:55,070 --> 00:08:57,260
[Miaose Dyeing Workshop]

142
00:09:24,350 --> 00:09:24,990
Ami.

143
00:09:26,430 --> 00:09:27,790
Is Song Ami here?

144
00:09:36,550 --> 00:09:38,270
You look so beautiful

145
00:09:39,710 --> 00:09:41,150
under the light of Taiyin.

146
00:09:41,150 --> 00:09:42,070
I thought

147
00:09:42,900 --> 00:09:44,380
you'd never come back.

148
00:09:45,900 --> 00:09:46,780
How could I?

149
00:09:51,910 --> 00:09:53,710
I don't want to see you like this.

150
00:09:56,030 --> 00:09:56,670
Come in.

151
00:10:16,310 --> 00:10:16,870
Right.

152
00:10:17,750 --> 00:10:18,510
This is it.

153
00:10:19,070 --> 00:10:20,110
With these 4 maps,

154
00:10:20,960 --> 00:10:22,870
it won't be long before

155
00:10:23,030 --> 00:10:24,710
the state government's army marches into Mount Taiyin

156
00:10:24,710 --> 00:10:27,110
and exterminates Taiyin Sect completely.

157
00:10:27,310 --> 00:10:27,910
Xijun.

158
00:10:28,550 --> 00:10:30,220
You've made another great contribution.

159
00:10:30,220 --> 00:10:32,930
This is what you got from your risky trip into the mountains.

160
00:10:32,930 --> 00:10:34,860
I just drew a few strokes in a hurry.

161
00:10:34,990 --> 00:10:37,520
I wouldn't consider it as some contribution.

162
00:10:38,020 --> 00:10:39,290
Let me see, let me see.

163
00:10:45,110 --> 00:10:45,790
Xijun.

164
00:10:46,190 --> 00:10:48,670
Lu Lingfeng showed no fear in the face of danger

165
00:10:48,670 --> 00:10:50,280
and made up something called

166
00:10:50,310 --> 00:10:52,350
the Map of Western Region's Troop Locations.

167
00:10:52,350 --> 00:10:54,260
Not only did he confuse the enemy,

168
00:10:54,340 --> 00:10:55,470
but he also got us

169
00:10:55,510 --> 00:10:58,630
such a detailed Arming Map of Taiyin in return.

170
00:10:59,190 --> 00:10:59,920
Impressive.

171
00:10:59,990 --> 00:11:01,050
Truly impressive.

172
00:11:02,070 --> 00:11:03,870
He reminds me of my younger self.

173
00:11:19,190 --> 00:11:19,920
Lu Lingfeng.

174
00:11:20,310 --> 00:11:22,350
It has been confirmed that you are here.

175
00:11:22,350 --> 00:11:24,410
Come out and surrender immediately.

176
00:11:24,690 --> 00:11:25,680
Who is it?

177
00:11:25,710 --> 00:11:27,190
Making so much noise...

178
00:11:28,380 --> 00:11:29,840
Listen up, people inside.

179
00:11:29,870 --> 00:11:30,430
The arrow

180
00:11:30,820 --> 00:11:31,950
is on the bowstring.

181
00:11:32,390 --> 00:11:34,050
Send Lu Lingfeng out quickly.

182
00:11:37,590 --> 00:11:38,720
I'll count to three.

183
00:11:39,550 --> 00:11:41,350
If Lu Lingfeng doesn't come out,

184
00:11:41,390 --> 00:11:44,520
be prepared to be pierced by tens of thousands of arrows.

185
00:11:45,590 --> 00:11:46,300
Three.

186
00:11:49,950 --> 00:11:50,670
Two.

187
00:11:55,780 --> 00:11:56,430
One.

188
00:12:02,210 --> 00:12:03,680
It's you, Minister Ma.

189
00:12:03,900 --> 00:12:06,030
What brings you here so early in the morning?

190
00:12:06,030 --> 00:12:08,150
Come on. Come in for some tea.

191
00:12:08,470 --> 00:12:09,150
Su Wuming.

192
00:12:09,550 --> 00:12:11,270
I'm not here to exchange pleasantries with you.

193
00:12:11,270 --> 00:12:13,670
Tell Lu Lingfeng to come out and surrender.

194
00:12:13,670 --> 00:12:14,330
Otherwise,

195
00:12:14,790 --> 00:12:16,320
there'll be consequences.

196
00:12:21,670 --> 00:12:22,310
Ma Meng.

197
00:12:23,650 --> 00:12:25,960
I'm Su Wuming, disciple of Detective Di.

198
00:12:25,980 --> 00:12:27,980
May I have a word with you in private?

199
00:12:31,070 --> 00:12:32,730
You are Di Renjie's disciple?

200
00:12:33,270 --> 00:12:35,110
I, Su, am incompetent.

201
00:12:35,790 --> 00:12:36,740
At this critical moment,

202
00:12:36,740 --> 00:12:38,710
I have to invoke my respected teacher's name.

203
00:12:38,710 --> 00:12:39,910
Please, Minister Ma.

204
00:12:41,570 --> 00:12:42,970
Come inside for some tea.

205
00:12:56,910 --> 00:12:58,240
Don't shoot the arrows.

206
00:13:07,030 --> 00:13:08,680
I've held Ma Meng,

207
00:13:08,710 --> 00:13:10,260
Judicial Adjutant of Hanzhou, hostage.

208
00:13:10,260 --> 00:13:11,670
If you don't want him to die,

209
00:13:11,670 --> 00:13:12,590
make way.

210
00:13:13,220 --> 00:13:13,860
Make way!

211
00:13:14,790 --> 00:13:16,510
Make way! Come on, make way!

212
00:13:32,510 --> 00:13:34,240
[Long's Residence]

213
00:13:42,270 --> 00:13:42,910
Move!

214
00:13:54,510 --> 00:13:55,870
What are you waiting for? Run!

215
00:13:55,870 --> 00:13:56,750
Come on, hurry.

216
00:13:59,210 --> 00:14:00,810
Tell your men not to chase us.

217
00:14:01,390 --> 00:14:02,550
If you don't want to die,

218
00:14:02,550 --> 00:14:03,680
don't come after us.

219
00:14:05,150 --> 00:14:06,150
Don't chase them!

220
00:14:09,710 --> 00:14:11,040
Watch out for an ambush.

221
00:15:17,440 --> 00:15:18,970
What... What's wrong, Ami?

222
00:15:20,030 --> 00:15:21,030
I had a nightmare.

223
00:15:22,470 --> 00:15:23,350
It was so scary.

224
00:15:26,710 --> 00:15:27,510
I dreamed that

225
00:15:28,710 --> 00:15:30,310
you punched him to death,

226
00:15:32,710 --> 00:15:34,840
and his brain splattered everywhere.

227
00:15:38,190 --> 00:15:39,190
How could that be?

228
00:15:39,580 --> 00:15:40,630
Didn't you tell me

229
00:15:40,660 --> 00:15:42,590
he ran away to avoid the creditors?

230
00:15:43,360 --> 00:15:44,810
Come on, let me rub your feet.

231
00:15:44,810 --> 00:15:45,410
No need.

232
00:15:46,380 --> 00:15:47,780
I've seen with my own eyes

233
00:15:48,600 --> 00:15:50,930
that you punched someone to death before.

234
00:15:51,150 --> 00:15:51,950
I'm scared.

235
00:15:55,630 --> 00:15:56,470
Don't worry.

236
00:15:57,590 --> 00:15:58,920
I kill with my left hand,

237
00:15:59,110 --> 00:16:00,950
but I care for you with my right hand.

238
00:16:00,950 --> 00:16:02,080
Let me rub your feet.

239
00:16:02,250 --> 00:16:03,310
I'll be gentle.

240
00:16:08,350 --> 00:16:09,550
I have some good news.

241
00:16:10,110 --> 00:16:11,190
Do you want to know?

242
00:16:11,990 --> 00:16:12,590
What is it?

243
00:16:12,790 --> 00:16:14,350
I told you before that

244
00:16:14,910 --> 00:16:16,000
an army of 100,000 men

245
00:16:16,000 --> 00:16:17,830
is no match for a single brilliant general.

246
00:16:17,830 --> 00:16:18,510
Now,

247
00:16:19,030 --> 00:16:20,380
that brilliant general has come to me

248
00:16:20,380 --> 00:16:21,510
with a valuable map.

249
00:16:21,790 --> 00:16:22,790
With this map,

250
00:16:23,020 --> 00:16:27,550
I can gain the allegiance of thousands of troops and horses of the Western Region.

251
00:16:28,190 --> 00:16:30,050
I don't understand these things,

252
00:16:31,310 --> 00:16:33,040
and I don't want to know either.

253
00:16:54,550 --> 00:16:57,870
[Two hours ago]

254
00:17:07,349 --> 00:17:08,670
Why should I trust you?

255
00:17:10,270 --> 00:17:11,670
I'll entrust these 4 maps

256
00:17:12,000 --> 00:17:13,390
to you, Minister Ma.

257
00:17:14,200 --> 00:17:15,210
How do I know

258
00:17:15,910 --> 00:17:17,240
if they are real or fake?

259
00:17:17,470 --> 00:17:18,550
Lu Lingfeng risked his life

260
00:17:18,550 --> 00:17:19,950
to get these.

261
00:17:20,270 --> 00:17:21,470
How can you doubt him?

262
00:17:22,390 --> 00:17:24,550
That's what all liars say.

263
00:17:24,819 --> 00:17:26,150
-How could youâ€¦
-Xijun.

264
00:17:35,710 --> 00:17:37,210
Since Minister Ma doesn't even believe

265
00:17:37,210 --> 00:17:38,590
the Arming Map of Taiyin,

266
00:17:38,590 --> 00:17:39,650
he definitely won't recognize

267
00:17:39,650 --> 00:17:40,850
Censor Xie's letter.

268
00:17:41,110 --> 00:17:42,750
I want that other thing.

269
00:17:56,030 --> 00:17:58,090
This is Master Moshi's tongue relic.

270
00:17:58,230 --> 00:18:00,090
The other half of it is in Hanzhou.

271
00:18:00,470 --> 00:18:01,600
The first time we met

272
00:18:01,910 --> 00:18:03,110
was at Hui'an Temple.

273
00:18:03,270 --> 00:18:05,170
I, Lu, was entrusted by the sheriff of Shen County,

274
00:18:05,170 --> 00:18:06,170
Jiang Wei,

275
00:18:07,310 --> 00:18:08,950
to reunite the two halves of

276
00:18:09,590 --> 00:18:10,990
this ultimate treasure.

277
00:18:26,070 --> 00:18:27,610
I'm willing to entrust this treasure

278
00:18:27,610 --> 00:18:28,950
to you, Minister Ma.

279
00:18:30,470 --> 00:18:31,600
Can you trust me now?

280
00:18:33,750 --> 00:18:34,550
Please don't.

281
00:18:35,250 --> 00:18:38,250
Master Moshi's tongue relic is an ultimate treasure.

282
00:18:39,070 --> 00:18:40,200
Of course I, Ma Meng,

283
00:18:40,590 --> 00:18:42,350
am well aware of the value of it.

284
00:18:42,510 --> 00:18:43,840
You have this treasure,

285
00:18:44,170 --> 00:18:46,230
yet you didn't exchange it for money.

286
00:18:50,190 --> 00:18:50,790
I, Ma Meng,

287
00:18:51,630 --> 00:18:52,710
can trust you now.

288
00:18:55,590 --> 00:18:56,250
Sheriff Lu.

289
00:18:57,450 --> 00:18:58,710
I'll follow your plan.

290
00:18:59,470 --> 00:19:00,790
Sheriff Lu. Mr. Su.

291
00:19:01,070 --> 00:19:02,390
What's our plan next?

292
00:19:02,770 --> 00:19:03,830
Hand over the maps.

293
00:19:06,260 --> 00:19:08,110
Minister Ma, please hand the maps

294
00:19:08,110 --> 00:19:09,260
directly to the prefectural governor.

295
00:19:09,260 --> 00:19:10,790
As for how you obtained the maps,

296
00:19:10,790 --> 00:19:12,510
there's no need to mention me, Lu Lingfeng.

297
00:19:12,510 --> 00:19:14,770
The credit for wiping out the Taiyin Sect

298
00:19:15,510 --> 00:19:17,240
will all go to you, Minister Ma.

299
00:19:20,070 --> 00:19:20,730
Sheriff Lu.

300
00:19:22,030 --> 00:19:24,110
What kind of person do you think I am?

301
00:19:25,680 --> 00:19:26,540
Minister Ma.

302
00:19:27,710 --> 00:19:29,990
Lu Lingfeng is just worried that if the state government

303
00:19:29,990 --> 00:19:31,950
finds out about the origin of these maps,

304
00:19:31,950 --> 00:19:33,190
not only will they not believe it,

305
00:19:33,190 --> 00:19:34,950
but they'll also accuse him

306
00:19:34,980 --> 00:19:36,290
of colluding with the Taiyin Sect

307
00:19:36,290 --> 00:19:37,490
and punish him for it.

308
00:19:38,350 --> 00:19:39,550
How is that possible?

309
00:19:40,230 --> 00:19:42,430
Some things have happened in Chang'an.

310
00:19:43,440 --> 00:19:44,550
I can't explain it to you

311
00:19:44,550 --> 00:19:45,610
in just a few words.

312
00:19:45,670 --> 00:19:47,590
Just do as Lu Lingfeng says.

313
00:19:47,790 --> 00:19:48,990
The people of Hanzhou

314
00:19:49,510 --> 00:19:50,840
will be grateful to you.

315
00:20:03,710 --> 00:20:04,440
Minister Ma.

316
00:20:04,530 --> 00:20:05,430
Please wait.

317
00:20:07,190 --> 00:20:07,920
Minister Ma.

318
00:20:08,750 --> 00:20:10,790
I have one more request.

319
00:20:11,270 --> 00:20:12,050
Please go ahead, Mr. Su.

320
00:20:12,050 --> 00:20:13,050
Here's the thing.

321
00:20:13,110 --> 00:20:14,510
I'm looking for a person.

322
00:20:15,080 --> 00:20:16,680
To be precise, a dead person,

323
00:20:16,700 --> 00:20:18,560
who died just a couple of days ago.

324
00:20:18,950 --> 00:20:20,540
I know you're busy

325
00:20:20,540 --> 00:20:21,910
and you have great responsibilities on your shoulders.

326
00:20:21,910 --> 00:20:23,790
But could you spare me a few men?

327
00:20:23,950 --> 00:20:25,110
I need to find

328
00:20:25,110 --> 00:20:27,440
that person's corpse as soon as possible.

329
00:20:28,230 --> 00:20:28,750
Okay.

330
00:20:29,350 --> 00:20:30,430
I will put

331
00:20:30,510 --> 00:20:31,740
all the trusted undercover detectives in Hanzhou City

332
00:20:31,740 --> 00:20:33,030
at your disposal, Mr. Su.

333
00:20:33,030 --> 00:20:36,050
[Troop Locations and Arming Map of Mount Taiyin]

334
00:20:36,310 --> 00:20:38,310
It's depicted in such detail.

335
00:20:38,910 --> 00:20:39,950
Who drew this?

336
00:20:42,700 --> 00:20:45,710
It was drawn by an undercover detective who I've been cultivating for a long time.

337
00:20:45,710 --> 00:20:47,950
He pretended to join them a few months ago.

338
00:20:47,950 --> 00:20:49,150
After many twists and turns,

339
00:20:49,150 --> 00:20:50,260
he finally managed to get into

340
00:20:50,260 --> 00:20:51,670
the heartland of Mount Taiyin

341
00:20:51,670 --> 00:20:53,510
and got a clear picture of

342
00:20:53,870 --> 00:20:55,200
the lair of Taiyin Sect.

343
00:20:56,750 --> 00:20:57,400
What about Lu Lingfeng,

344
00:20:57,400 --> 00:20:58,390
who was kidnapped by the members of Taiyin Sect

345
00:20:58,390 --> 00:20:59,470
yesterday?

346
00:20:59,880 --> 00:21:00,990
My undercover detective said that

347
00:21:00,990 --> 00:21:02,550
he already defected to Taiyin Sect

348
00:21:02,550 --> 00:21:03,750
and gained their appreciation.

349
00:21:03,750 --> 00:21:05,830
He now lives on Mount Taiyin.

350
00:21:06,790 --> 00:21:08,990
So what's your plan, Minister Ma?

351
00:21:09,980 --> 00:21:11,710
Although we've got these maps,

352
00:21:11,770 --> 00:21:12,690
I don't think

353
00:21:12,990 --> 00:21:15,160
we should rush into the mountain to encircle and suppress them.

354
00:21:15,160 --> 00:21:16,590
We should first order the nearby prefectures and counties

355
00:21:16,590 --> 00:21:19,110
to cooperate in investigating the Taiyin Sect's accomplices,

356
00:21:19,110 --> 00:21:20,270
and figure out how many people

357
00:21:20,270 --> 00:21:21,590
are there who are determined

358
00:21:21,590 --> 00:21:22,650
to rebel with them.

359
00:21:22,970 --> 00:21:24,320
We should also mobilize

360
00:21:24,350 --> 00:21:25,350
all the huntsmen in nearby prefectures and counties

361
00:21:25,350 --> 00:21:27,590
to guard against numerous beasts on Mount Taiyin.

362
00:21:27,590 --> 00:21:29,190
Then, when the time is right,

363
00:21:29,190 --> 00:21:30,270
we'll join forces with the Commandery

364
00:21:30,270 --> 00:21:31,480
and send troops together.

365
00:21:31,480 --> 00:21:33,590
We will definitely wipe out Mount Taiyin in one attempt

366
00:21:33,590 --> 00:21:36,250
and bring hundreds of years of peace to Hanzhou.

367
00:21:37,120 --> 00:21:37,990
Minister Ma.

368
00:21:38,380 --> 00:21:39,650
Haven't you always advocated

369
00:21:39,650 --> 00:21:41,270
marching into the mountains to suppress the bandits?

370
00:21:41,270 --> 00:21:42,510
Now that we've got the maps,

371
00:21:42,510 --> 00:21:44,150
why are you not in a hurry anymore?

372
00:21:44,150 --> 00:21:45,590
You said you want to wait for the right time.

373
00:21:45,590 --> 00:21:46,650
Why should we wait?

374
00:21:49,070 --> 00:21:50,630
We are Hanzhou's officials.

375
00:21:50,630 --> 00:21:51,390
Taiyin Sect

376
00:21:51,510 --> 00:21:52,920
is like a knife hanging

377
00:21:52,950 --> 00:21:53,810
over our heads.

378
00:21:53,830 --> 00:21:54,910
If we keep delaying the suppression,

379
00:21:54,910 --> 00:21:55,890
how can we not be ashamed,

380
00:21:55,890 --> 00:21:57,490
taking money from the court?

381
00:21:59,110 --> 00:22:00,310
Time waits for no one.

382
00:22:00,790 --> 00:22:02,510
Let's enter the mountain today.

383
00:22:02,510 --> 00:22:03,240
Minister Ma.

384
00:22:04,000 --> 00:22:06,400
This is your chance to make an achievement.

385
00:22:07,470 --> 00:22:07,960
But...

386
00:22:08,370 --> 00:22:09,170
But we...

387
00:22:10,380 --> 00:22:11,830
According to the map,

388
00:22:12,010 --> 00:22:13,730
the Taiyin Sect members on the mountain

389
00:22:13,730 --> 00:22:14,910
are not few in number.

390
00:22:14,910 --> 00:22:16,780
We are in shortage of troops.

391
00:22:17,090 --> 00:22:18,760
Bring all the soldiers that

392
00:22:18,780 --> 00:22:19,950
the state government sent to Hanzhou Granary back.

393
00:22:19,950 --> 00:22:21,190
Redeploy half of the guards

394
00:22:21,190 --> 00:22:22,390
from each of the four city gates.

395
00:22:22,390 --> 00:22:22,990
I'll also

396
00:22:24,020 --> 00:22:25,650
deploy all the soldiers

397
00:22:26,190 --> 00:22:28,050
stationing Hui'an Temple to you.

398
00:22:28,550 --> 00:22:29,410
Governor Liao.

399
00:22:29,830 --> 00:22:32,030
How can we leave the relic unprotected?

400
00:22:32,630 --> 00:22:34,230
Maybe we shouldn't withdraw the soldiers

401
00:22:34,230 --> 00:22:35,360
from Hui'an Temple.

402
00:22:35,510 --> 00:22:36,840
They must be withdrawn.

403
00:22:36,910 --> 00:22:38,770
Although the relic is a treasure,

404
00:22:38,840 --> 00:22:40,760
wiping out Taiyin Sect

405
00:22:41,230 --> 00:22:43,790
is the top priority of Hanzhou.

406
00:22:47,350 --> 00:22:48,080
Minister Ma.

407
00:22:49,000 --> 00:22:51,110
I'm giving you command of all the troops

408
00:22:51,110 --> 00:22:52,470
I can mobilize in Hanzhou.

409
00:22:52,470 --> 00:22:53,800
Although you're young,

410
00:22:53,990 --> 00:22:55,950
you bravely take on a heavy responsibility today.

411
00:22:55,950 --> 00:22:58,680
You will surely have great success in the future.

412
00:22:59,230 --> 00:23:01,230
Thank you for your trust, Governor.

413
00:23:08,140 --> 00:23:09,530
[Prefectural Governor's Residence]

414
00:23:13,430 --> 00:23:14,040
Ma Meng.

415
00:23:14,870 --> 00:23:16,900
I don't care whether Lu Lingfeng, who's on Mount Taiyin,

416
00:23:16,900 --> 00:23:18,710
is dead or alive.

417
00:23:19,270 --> 00:23:21,630
You must bring back that half piece of tongue relic on him

418
00:23:21,630 --> 00:23:23,150
back to me.

419
00:23:25,060 --> 00:23:26,460
Rest assured, Governor.

420
00:23:35,130 --> 00:23:39,390
[Hanzhou]

421
00:23:44,540 --> 00:23:45,610
[Long's Fur Shop]

422
00:23:48,770 --> 00:23:49,480
Take care.

423
00:23:54,240 --> 00:23:55,390
Where are we going next?

424
00:23:55,390 --> 00:23:56,450
Jiufang Pavilion.

425
00:23:56,850 --> 00:23:58,180
There's a casino there.

426
00:23:58,510 --> 00:23:59,660
You can drink as much as you want for free

427
00:23:59,660 --> 00:24:01,190
as long as you gamble there.

428
00:24:01,260 --> 00:24:03,590
Plus, you'll be accompanied by beautiful dancers.

429
00:24:03,590 --> 00:24:06,190
I heard their dancing is absolutely stunning.

430
00:24:07,690 --> 00:24:10,280
Well then, I'll enjoy it.

431
00:24:11,760 --> 00:24:13,880
You... you're coming in with me?

432
00:24:14,990 --> 00:24:16,390
What do you think?

433
00:24:16,960 --> 00:24:17,760
Right, right.

434
00:24:18,000 --> 00:24:19,390
Let's go in together.

435
00:24:26,070 --> 00:24:27,100
Master Moshi.

436
00:24:26,520 --> 00:24:29,570
[Diamond Sutra]

437
00:24:28,050 --> 00:24:30,450
Today is your birthday in the mortal world.

438
00:24:30,470 --> 00:24:33,470
I, your disciple, am here to celebrate your birthday.

439
00:24:33,870 --> 00:24:35,230
Please bless me,

440
00:24:35,630 --> 00:24:37,760
so that I can obtain your tongue relic.

441
00:24:38,540 --> 00:24:41,590
From now on, I will

442
00:24:42,590 --> 00:24:44,230
serve you

443
00:24:44,910 --> 00:24:46,510
whole-heartedly every day.

444
00:24:53,180 --> 00:24:54,020
This time,

445
00:24:54,510 --> 00:24:56,820
I want 5 gold coins.

446
00:24:57,190 --> 00:24:58,430
5 gold coins?

447
00:24:59,620 --> 00:25:00,430
Are you crazy?

448
00:25:00,530 --> 00:25:01,240
I've never seen so much money

449
00:25:01,240 --> 00:25:02,290
in my entire life.

450
00:25:03,610 --> 00:25:04,990
Someone drew

451
00:25:04,990 --> 00:25:06,720
the arming map of Mount Taiyin.

452
00:25:06,790 --> 00:25:09,270
The entire Hanzhou is mobilizing troops.

453
00:25:09,670 --> 00:25:11,730
If you tell your higher-ups the news,

454
00:25:12,390 --> 00:25:14,050
is it worth 5 gold coins or not?

455
00:25:16,310 --> 00:25:17,270
If not, forget it.

456
00:25:17,270 --> 00:25:18,980
Don't think about getting any information

457
00:25:18,980 --> 00:25:20,180
from me ever again.

458
00:25:24,190 --> 00:25:25,070
Don't go.

459
00:25:25,850 --> 00:25:27,110
The higher-ups seem to have anticipated

460
00:25:27,110 --> 00:25:28,510
that you would have important information today.

461
00:25:28,510 --> 00:25:30,970
They actually asked me to bring 5 gold coins.

462
00:25:55,060 --> 00:25:56,630
When did you arrive?

463
00:25:58,510 --> 00:25:59,350
Master.

464
00:26:00,660 --> 00:26:01,670
I was wrong.

465
00:26:02,790 --> 00:26:04,260
Is this about Lu Lingfeng?

466
00:26:05,910 --> 00:26:07,310
How did you know, Master?

467
00:26:09,080 --> 00:26:10,280
Do you think

468
00:26:10,310 --> 00:26:12,350
you are my only source of information?

469
00:26:12,350 --> 00:26:13,990
I'm afraid you only know

470
00:26:14,480 --> 00:26:16,140
one side of the story, Master.

471
00:26:16,550 --> 00:26:17,630
They've already drawn

472
00:26:17,630 --> 00:26:19,360
the arming map of the mountain.

473
00:26:19,830 --> 00:26:21,290
Taiyin Sect's stronghold

474
00:26:21,630 --> 00:26:22,710
is in grave danger.

475
00:26:23,630 --> 00:26:25,310
I, Linghu Shuo, have made a grave mistake.

476
00:26:25,310 --> 00:26:26,870
Please execute me, Master.

477
00:26:27,190 --> 00:26:27,700
I...

478
00:26:53,080 --> 00:26:54,910
If it weren't for you,

479
00:26:55,710 --> 00:26:58,000
Taiyin Sect wouldn't be

480
00:26:58,030 --> 00:26:59,430
what it's like today.

481
00:27:14,220 --> 00:27:16,110
Why did you only use your left fist?

482
00:27:16,110 --> 00:27:16,640
Who is it?

483
00:27:23,790 --> 00:27:25,320
It's none of your business.

484
00:27:26,110 --> 00:27:27,170
It's been 10 years.

485
00:27:27,910 --> 00:27:29,840
Whenever the moonlight is bright,

486
00:27:30,020 --> 00:27:31,930
you would practice boxing here.

487
00:27:32,670 --> 00:27:34,400
I've kept count of all the trees

488
00:27:34,800 --> 00:27:36,400
you knocked down

489
00:27:36,430 --> 00:27:38,700
and all the rocks

490
00:27:39,390 --> 00:27:41,120
you broke in the back mountain.

491
00:27:41,590 --> 00:27:42,200
What?

492
00:27:42,710 --> 00:27:44,590
Are you a monk from Hui'an Temple?

493
00:27:45,170 --> 00:27:47,170
Do you want me to pay for the damages?

494
00:27:47,410 --> 00:27:48,270
I have no money.

495
00:27:48,470 --> 00:27:50,560
Why do you only use your left fist?

496
00:27:51,950 --> 00:27:53,070
Old monk.

497
00:27:53,350 --> 00:27:54,710
I'm not telling you.

498
00:28:10,390 --> 00:28:10,980
This...

499
00:28:12,240 --> 00:28:12,830
Old monk.

500
00:28:13,510 --> 00:28:14,570
You are so skilled.

501
00:28:15,430 --> 00:28:17,030
How did you train your left fist?

502
00:28:17,030 --> 00:28:18,560
I learned it from my master.

503
00:28:19,350 --> 00:28:20,670
His surname is Duan.

504
00:28:21,790 --> 00:28:22,550
Duan?

505
00:28:23,680 --> 00:28:26,080
Could it be Duan Gui who dominated Hanzhou?

506
00:28:27,780 --> 00:28:28,390
Master.

507
00:28:28,990 --> 00:28:31,050
Would you accept me as your disciple?

508
00:28:33,810 --> 00:28:34,710
Linghu Shuo.

509
00:28:34,730 --> 00:28:35,170
Yes.

510
00:28:35,590 --> 00:28:36,500
You are the only son

511
00:28:36,500 --> 00:28:38,960
of the owner of Jiufang Pavilion in the city.

512
00:28:38,990 --> 00:28:40,850
Your family is not short of money.

513
00:28:41,150 --> 00:28:43,270
Your father is also good at socializing.

514
00:28:43,270 --> 00:28:45,070
It wouldn't be difficult for him

515
00:28:45,320 --> 00:28:47,250
to find you a job in the government.

516
00:28:47,870 --> 00:28:49,200
Work in the government?

517
00:28:49,710 --> 00:28:51,370
Be loyal to Chang'an's court,

518
00:28:51,380 --> 00:28:53,180
and create a prosperous era for the Li family?

519
00:28:53,180 --> 00:28:53,960
If so, how could I, Linghu Shuo,

520
00:28:53,960 --> 00:28:55,590
live up to the expectations of my ancestors?

521
00:28:55,590 --> 00:28:58,030
The Linghus are the descendants of King Wen of Zhou state.

522
00:28:58,030 --> 00:28:59,130
I'm exceptionally talented

523
00:28:59,130 --> 00:29:00,870
and have an outstanding appearance.

524
00:29:00,870 --> 00:29:02,140
I should be

525
00:29:02,550 --> 00:29:03,630
establishing my own power

526
00:29:03,630 --> 00:29:05,270
and achieving great feats like Duan Gui.

527
00:29:05,270 --> 00:29:07,530
Only in this way can my life not be in vain.

528
00:29:08,830 --> 00:29:10,230
Ambitious.

529
00:29:10,740 --> 00:29:11,230
Master.

530
00:29:11,660 --> 00:29:12,610
To be honest,

531
00:29:12,980 --> 00:29:15,040
I've always been better at studying than others since I was little.

532
00:29:15,040 --> 00:29:16,110
But when it comes to the Four Books and Five Classics,

533
00:29:16,110 --> 00:29:17,270
or the writings of sages,

534
00:29:17,270 --> 00:29:18,870
I couldn't stand reading them,

535
00:29:18,870 --> 00:29:20,270
except Duan Gui's books.

536
00:29:20,310 --> 00:29:21,790
It's only his books

537
00:29:22,110 --> 00:29:23,590
that I never get tired of reading.

538
00:29:23,590 --> 00:29:25,850
Especially after he broke his right arm.

539
00:29:27,310 --> 00:29:29,710
He killed many generals of the court of Tang

540
00:29:29,710 --> 00:29:32,150
with his left hand alone.

541
00:29:33,470 --> 00:29:35,000
Every time I read that part,

542
00:29:35,080 --> 00:29:37,140
my blood would race with excitement.

543
00:29:37,670 --> 00:29:38,510
At that time,

544
00:29:39,030 --> 00:29:40,870
I was already in my 90s.

545
00:29:42,640 --> 00:29:44,700
What I was most anxious about was that

546
00:29:45,280 --> 00:29:47,280
I couldn't convince the sect leader

547
00:29:48,030 --> 00:29:50,790
to revitalize the Taiyin Sect.

548
00:29:53,950 --> 00:29:55,590
If it weren't for you,

549
00:29:57,530 --> 00:29:58,640
how could we have

550
00:29:58,670 --> 00:30:00,630
reassembled the Mountain Gods

551
00:30:00,870 --> 00:30:03,000
and recruited our members after that?

552
00:30:03,510 --> 00:30:04,910
In just 3 short years,

553
00:30:06,270 --> 00:30:08,270
we reunited the fragmented

554
00:30:08,290 --> 00:30:09,540
Taiyin Sect

555
00:30:10,430 --> 00:30:12,160
and made it great again.

556
00:30:13,710 --> 00:30:15,680
Thank you, Master, for remembering my contributions.

557
00:30:15,680 --> 00:30:16,100
But

558
00:30:16,590 --> 00:30:18,320
the sect rules are inviolable.

559
00:30:18,510 --> 00:30:20,170
I have to be punished by death.

560
00:30:20,670 --> 00:30:21,400
No.

561
00:30:24,830 --> 00:30:26,090
This might actually be

562
00:30:28,100 --> 00:30:30,830
our opportunity.

563
00:30:49,070 --> 00:30:49,620
Master.

